# To allow to fall.
#: ''Don't '''drop''' that plate!''
# To get rid of.
#: ''I '''dropped''' 10 pounds and an obnoxious fiance.''
# To eject, to remove.
#: ''I've been '''dropped''' from the football team.''
# To fail to respond to an argument.
